reviewText: Had my husband and I rolling with laughter! Very happy we bought this. We love comedy and we especially love clean humor!
Biscuit is hilarious ! I love his jokes and can't get them out if my mind he so funny I enjoyed his show

Expecting a good follow-on to It's Latter-Day Night Live Comedy I was sadly disappointed.  My family and I set through the entire comedy monolog with the hope that it would get better. Sadly it did not.  Save your money!
I am a "Mormon" and my husband is not - we both got some great laughs and hope he does another DVD!
